		{ ref: `Philippians 4:6`, slug: `philippians`, ch: 4, text: `Do not be anxious about anything, but in everything, by prayer and thanksgiving, let your requests be made known to your Father.`, note: `The anxiety has a place to go — straight to a Father who is listening and isn't overwhelmed.` },
