		{ heading: `An identity nothing on campus can shake`, bodyHtml: `Your worth isn't your GPA or your follower count. You are <a href="https://fathersheartbible.com/read/psalms/139" style="color: var(--color-brand);" class="hover:underline">fearfully and wonderfully made</a> and <a href="https://fathersheartbible.com/read/isaiah/43" style="color: var(--color-brand);" class="hover:underline">called by name</a> — His, before you achieve a thing.` },
		{ heading: `Rest for the all-nighter season`, bodyHtml: `When you're running on caffeine and four hours of sleep, your Father says <a href="https://fathersheartbible.com/read/matthew/11" style="color: var(--color-brand);" class="hover:underline">"come to Me and I will give you rest"</a> — a peace no planner can manufacture.` },
