	whyBlocks={[
		{ heading: `You meet God as a Father, not a rulebook`, bodyHtml: `If the version of God you grew up with is falling apart in college, that might be a good thing — because a distant rule-giver was never the real One. The Father's Heart Bible™ reveals God as <em>Father</em> wherever Scripture does, from <a href="https://fathersheartbible.com/read/genesis/1" style="color: var(--color-brand);" class="hover:underline">Genesis 1</a> on — the kind of love you can actually come home to.` },
		{ heading: `It fits a student's actual life`, bodyHtml: `Free to <a href="https://fathersheartbible.com/read" style="color: var(--color-brand);" class="hover:underline">read online</a> with audio on every chapter — no account, no purchase, no app. Listen walking to class, read a few minutes before bed, or hit play at 2am when the anxiety won't quit.` },
